  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Check out my next project — <strong>Little Astronaut</strong>, a top-down sci-fi puzzle game where a mysterious fungus infects a base.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add it to your Steam wishlist!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518110/extras/12d33039f3db605f6b2663bac7a55d4b.avif?t=1773071986\" width=1232 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exit the Abyss</strong> is a psychological horror game set in an abandoned, haunted hospital. The player controls a young man who, after his death, becomes trapped in an alternate hospital. To return to the world of the living, he must solve mysterious tasks and endure mentally exhausting trials.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is a slow-paced, atmospheric horror experience that focuses on psychological tension, oppressive ambiance, and environmental storytelling. There are no dialogues or human voices—the story unfolds solely through the eerie environment, unsettling events, and hidden details.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(Exit The Abyss is a short, roughly 30–35 minute walk with a few puzzles — nothing more, nothing less.)</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 <strong>Atmospheric psychological horror</strong> – Pulls you into a dark and oppressive world, creating a constant sense of uncertainty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518110/extras/5cd5f0d593ffa6438a9b56207f6a2718.poster.avif?t=1773071986\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518110/extras/5cd5f0d593ffa6438a9b56207f6a2718.webm?t=1773071986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518110/extras/5cd5f0d593ffa6438a9b56207f6a2718.mp4?t=1773071986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>🔹 <strong>Walking simulator with minimalist puzzles</strong> – No complex riddles; the game focuses on exploration and visual storytelling.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 <strong>Minimalist yet haunting visuals</strong> – Enhances the feeling of isolation and fear.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518110/extras/60fb7aba76f9a2d06825aca6f27110da.poster.avif?t=1773071986\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518110/extras/60fb7aba76f9a2d06825aca6f27110da.webm?t=1773071986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518110/extras/60fb7aba76f9a2d06825aca6f27110da.mp4?t=1773071986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>🔹 <strong>Environmental storytelling</strong> – Hidden messages, ominous details, and disturbing events lead you toward the final resolution.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 <strong>Single-player, first-person horror</strong> – Combines liminal space aesthetics with psychological horror elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518110/extras/d9c1c81027691453bbd618f1ff2f8ee8.poster.avif?t=1773071986\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518110/extras/d9c1c81027691453bbd618f1ff2f8ee8.webm?t=1773071986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518110/extras/d9c1c81027691453bbd618f1ff2f8ee8.mp4?t=1773071986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you enjoy psychological horror and liminal space games like <i>Layers of Fear, SOMA, The Stanley Parable, The Exit 8, Paratopic, Anemoiapolis,</i> or <i>Lost in Vivo</i>, then <strong>Exit the Abyss</strong> will be a perfect choice for you!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Check out my next project — <strong>Little Astronaut</strong>, a top-down sci-fi puzzle game where a mysterious fungus infects a base.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add it to your Steam wishlist!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518110/extras/12d33039f3db605f6b2663bac7a55d4b.avif?t=1773071986\" width=1232 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exit the Abyss</strong> is a psychological horror game set in an abandoned, haunted hospital. The player controls a young man who, after his death, becomes trapped in an alternate hospital. To return to the world of the living, he must solve mysterious tasks and endure mentally exhausting trials.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is a slow-paced, atmospheric horror experience that focuses on psychological tension, oppressive ambiance, and environmental storytelling. There are no dialogues or human voices—the story unfolds solely through the eerie environment, unsettling events, and hidden details.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(Exit The Abyss is a short, roughly 30–35 minute walk with a few puzzles — nothing more, nothing less.)</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 <strong>Atmospheric psychological horror</strong> – Pulls you into a dark and oppressive world, creating a constant sense of uncertainty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518110/extras/5cd5f0d593ffa6438a9b56207f6a2718.poster.avif?t=1773071986\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518110/extras/5cd5f0d593ffa6438a9b56207f6a2718.webm?t=1773071986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518110/extras/5cd5f0d593ffa6438a9b56207f6a2718.mp4?t=1773071986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>🔹 <strong>Walking simulator with minimalist puzzles</strong> – No complex riddles; the game focuses on exploration and visual storytelling.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 <strong>Minimalist yet haunting visuals</strong> – Enhances the feeling of isolation and fear.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518110/extras/60fb7aba76f9a2d06825aca6f27110da.poster.avif?t=1773071986\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518110/extras/60fb7aba76f9a2d06825aca6f27110da.webm?t=1773071986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518110/extras/60fb7aba76f9a2d06825aca6f27110da.mp4?t=1773071986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>🔹 <strong>Environmental storytelling</strong> – Hidden messages, ominous details, and disturbing events lead you toward the final resolution.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 <strong>Single-player, first-person horror</strong> – Combines liminal space aesthetics with psychological horror elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518110/extras/d9c1c81027691453bbd618f1ff2f8ee8.poster.avif?t=1773071986\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518110/extras/d9c1c81027691453bbd618f1ff2f8ee8.webm?t=1773071986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3518110/extras/d9c1c81027691453bbd618f1ff2f8ee8.mp4?t=1773071986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you enjoy psychological horror and liminal space games like <i>Layers of Fear, SOMA, The Stanley Parable, The Exit 8, Paratopic, Anemoiapolis,</i> or <i>Lost in Vivo</i>, then <strong>Exit the Abyss</strong> will be a perfect choice for you!</p>",
